<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="consist-vi">consist <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'sɪst/    美 /kən'sɪst/  </p>
<p>[不用于进行时和被动语态]</p>
<h2 id="_1">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="consist-in">consist in</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>在于；存在于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Happiness consists in contentment.
知足常乐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Success consists in the ability to continue efforts through failures.
成功在于百折不挠。</p><footer>2014 福建书面表达</footer></div>

<h3 id="consist-of">consist of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>由…构成；由…组成：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How many countries does the UK consist of?
大不列颠联合王国由多少个国家组成？</p><footer>人教⑤ – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Life consists of not only sunshine but also storms.
生活不仅有阳光，还有风雨。</p><footer>2008 辽宁书面表达改</footer></div></div>